Email notification logic is inverted in `sendAddGuestsEmails`: newly-added guests (emails in `newGuests`) are sent `AttendeeScheduledEmail`, while existing attendees are sent `AttendeeAddGuestsEmail`, which is the opposite of the intended behavior. Evidence (email-manager.ts):
```ts
if (newGuests.includes(attendee.email)) {
  return sendEmail(() => new AttendeeScheduledEmail(calendarEvent, attendee));
} else {
  return sendEmail(() => new AttendeeAddGuestsEmail(calendarEvent, attendee));
}
```
